Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.96,0:00:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The burgeoning metropolis\Nof Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.83,0:00:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of those who lurk in the\Ndark underbelly of this city...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.80,0:00:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...some cower in the\Ndarkness itself...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.00,0:00:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...while others seek pleasure\Nto escape the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.14,0:00:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This man may very well have been\Na victim of the forces of darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.85,0:00:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ln response to such unusual cases,\NPolice Chief Kanzaki had...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...gathered up a group of people\Nwith unusual abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man who regularly\Nrisks his life in movie stunts...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.49,0:00:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in order to forget his past...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Koji Yamada is a\Nmember of that team.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.87,0:00:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This loner of a man found some\Nhappiness in his friendly relations...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with a female neighbor\Nand her son.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.91,0:00:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koji was chosen as partner to Jun\Nwho has the clairvoyant ability...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.61,0:00:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to see the last moments of a victim's\Nlife as she climaxes during sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.81,0:01:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sex was supposed to be\Nloveless and dry...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.62,0:01:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but Jun was mysteriously\Naroused and...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.69,0:01:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...had become\Nemotionally drawn to Koji.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.85,0:01:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.89,0:01:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the anguished soul of Koji...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who had taken the life of a\Nformer lover with his own hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.83,0:01:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was closed and unyielding.
