Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.24,0:01:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, their leader, Chief Kanzaki\Nhad been monitoring the lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.41,0:01:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...of the team members\Nfor some unknown reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.35,0:01:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's the mysterious entity\Nthat oversees the murder...
