Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.28,0:37:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just have to wait at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.68,0:37:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want to stay with my Mother forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.15,0:37:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't mean you\Ncan go around killing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.28,0:37:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.22,0:37:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.55,0:37:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.59,0:37:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.26,0:37:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.10,0:37:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother...! Mother...!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.97,0:37:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jun...!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.24,0:37:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, l got the bad guys!\Nl got them for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.31,0:37:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? What a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.65,0:37:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.65,0:37:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.99,0:37:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This could be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.56,0:37:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.83,0:37:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His mind's resonating with the son's\Nand the son is starting to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.66,0:37:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.86,0:38:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman who went after\Nhim has done something.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.74,0:38:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.54,0:38:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.45,0:38:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not my Mother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.79,0:38:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother...? Mother...?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.76,0:38:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Mother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.79,0:38:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.13,0:38:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother...!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.46,0:38:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want you to disappear from my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.96,0:38:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother... Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.93,0:38:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.95,0:38:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koji!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.62,0:38:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuta! Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.65,0:39:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Koji!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.58,0:39:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a crazy bastard, that Koji.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.28,0:39:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.25,0:39:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll be letting him know that\Nyou've done good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.95,0:40:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, have you made\Npreparations for the next?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.89,0:40:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.32,0:40:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.39,0:40:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.29,0:40:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pompous bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.83,0:40:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he doesn't even realize\Nthat he's being used.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.01,0:40:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old man was cleaning up after\Nthe mess left by his grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.11,0:40:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he was always\Nat the crime scene.
